{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017gpd3mVassBJNe374dtVcf","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# PPT Creation Agent\n     2→\n     3→Specialized HTML parser agent for PowerPoint slide generation. Minimal agent with no versioned prompts, flights, or filters.\n     4→\n     5→## Setup\n     6→\n     7→```env\n     8→OAGENT_AGENTID=ppt-creation-agent\n     9→```\n    10→\n    11→## Key Files\n    12→\n    13→| File | Purpose |\n    14→|------|---------|\n    15→| `src/ppt-creation-agent.ts` | Main agent implementation |\n    16→| `src/registry.ts` | Minimal registry (id, name, description only) |\n    17→\n    18→## Dependencies\n    19→\n    20→`@officeagent/core`, `@officeagent/message-protocol`\n    21→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VbaCZT2x5MAVT4SegakNyh","session_id":"98ef6066-2367-415b-b616-f95ed64be17a","uuid":"ea97b19a-4af3-4158-809c-d5b17c8e17be"}
