{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SiBTfVkPY3kVRr6QrLMyrW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Excel Agent - Developer Quick Reference\n     2→\n     3→## What This Agent Does\n     4→\n     5→Excel editing agent running in the OfficeAgent container.\n     6→Uses **GitHub Copilot SDK** for LLM orchestration and the **local tool** pattern for Office.js execution via the augloop proxy.\n     7→\n     8→The proxy (`excel-agent-container-proxy.ts` in augloop-workflows) forwards requests to this container agent and bridges local script execution back to the Excel client.\n     9→\n    10→## Architecture\n    11→\n    12→```\n    13→augloop proxy                           OfficeAgent Container\n    14→+--------------------+                  +-------------------------------+\n    15→| ContainerProxy     |    WebSocket     |  ExcelAgent (BaseAgent)       |\n    16→|                    | <--------------> |                               |\n    17→| sends ChatRequest  |                  |  CopilotBridge                |\n    18→| routes ScriptResp  |  ScriptRequest   |   - CopilotClient             |\n    19→|                    | <--------------  |   - CopilotSession            |\n    20→| ScriptBridge       |  ScriptResponse  |   - event subscriptions       |\n    21→|  -> Excel client   | -------------->  |                               |\n    22→|  -> result back    |                  |  ScriptExecutor               |\n    23→|                    |  QueryStatus     |   - promise-based req/res     |\n    24→| QueryStatusHandler | <--------------  |                               |\n    25→|  -> annotations    |                  |  EventAdapter                 |\n    26→|                    |  ChatResponse    |   - SDK events -> QueryStatus |\n    27→| ACK handling       | <--------------  |                               |\n    28→+--------------------+                  +-------------------------------+\n    29→```\n    30→\n    31→## Key Files\n    32→\n    33→| File | Purpose |\n    34→|------|---------|\n    35→| `src/excel-agent.ts` | Main agent class - wires CopilotBridge, ScriptExecutor, EventAdapter |\n    36→| `src/registry.ts` | Minimal agent config with Copilot SDK model settings |\n    37→| `src/types.ts` | ExcelRunLocalScript payloads, ScriptResult type |\n    38→| `src/protocol/script-executor.ts` | Promise-based script execution over WebSocket |\n    39→| `src/copilot/copilot-bridge.ts` | Copilot SDK session lifecycle + event subscriptions |\n    40→| `src/copilot/event-adapter.ts` | SDK events -> QueryStatus messages for the proxy |\n    41→| `src/copilot/system-prompt.ts` | ~760 line Office.js guidance prompt |\n    42→| `src/copilot/tools/interact-with-document.ts` | `excel_interact_document` tool definition |\n    43→| `src/copilot/tools/document-context.ts` | Workbook sampling script for context discovery |\n    44→\n    45→## Message Flow\n    46→\n    47→1. Proxy sends `ChatRequest` with query, queryId, conversationId\n    48→2. Agent sends `ChatResponse` ACK (`success: true`)\n    49→3. Agent runs document context discovery script via `ExcelRunLocalScriptRequest`\n    50→4. Agent creates Copilot SDK session with system prompt + document context\n    51→5. SDK streams events:\n    52→   - `reasoning_delta` -> `QueryStatus(FileCreated, chainOfThought.txt)`\n    53→   - `tool.execution_start` -> `QueryStatus(FileCreated, chainOfThought.txt)`\n    54→   - Tool `excel_interact_document` called -> `ExcelRunLocalScriptRequest` -> response -> return to SDK\n    55→   - `message_delta` -> `QueryStatus(FileCreated, chatMessage_N.txt)`\n    56→   - `session.idle` -> `QueryStatus(DocumentGenerated)`\n    57→6. Error -> `QueryStatus(DocumentGenerationFailed)`\n    58→\n    59→## Configuration\n    60→\n    61→### Flights\n    62→\n    63→| Flight Key | Effect |\n    64→|-----------|--------|\n    65→| `ExcelAgent.CopilotModel` | Override Copilot SDK model (default: `gpt-52-reasoning`) |\n    66→\n    67→## Dependencies\n    68→\n    69→| Package | What It Provides |\n    70→|---------|-----------------|\n    71→| `@github/copilot-sdk` | CopilotClient, CopilotSession, defineTool, approveAll |\n    72→| `@officeagent/core` | BaseAgent, SessionContext, wsManager, WebSocketRouter, logging |\n    73→| `@officeagent/message-protocol` | MessageType, QueryStatusType, QueryStatusPayload |\n    74→| `zod` | Tool parameter schema definitions |\n    75→\n    76→## Environment Requirements\n    77→\n    78→- `GITHUB_TOKEN` env var (or `gh auth login`) for Copilot SDK authentication\n    79→- `@github/copilot-sdk` npm package in container runtime\n    80→- Network access to GitHub API from container\n    81→\n    82→## Development\n    83→\n    84→```powershell\n    85→yarn build          # Build (gulp)\n    86→yarn test           # Unit tests\n    87→```\n    88→\n    89→Required `.env`:\n    90→```\n    91→OAGENT_AGENTID=excel-agent\n    92→GITHUB_TOKEN=<your-token>\n    93→```\n    94→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VbaCZT2x5MAVT4SegakNyh","session_id":"98ef6066-2367-415b-b616-f95ed64be17a","uuid":"bed32f34-d2f3-45db-8a38-69baa11d4ecc"}
