{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KKSiz7hf6aZwDCX6LNqNek","type":"tool_result","content":"---\nname: Word Document Suite\ndescription: Microsoft Word (.docx) document creation with intelligent content generation, themed formatting, and chart integration. It generates professional reports, proposals, and documents with automatic validation. This should be used when users need to work with Word documents for (1) Creating new .docx files with professional formatting and themed styling, (2) Generating reports, proposals, or business documents, (3) Creating documents from outlines or requirements, (4) Documents requiring charts and tables, or (5) Multi-page documents with Table of Contents and References\n---\n\n# Creating Word Documents\n\nTransform user requests into professional Word documents through a 5-phase workflow with page-wise parallel processing.\n\n# CRITICAL Environment Variables Instructions\n\nThere are environment variables used in prompts like  ${SKILLS_DIR}, ${OUTPUT_DIR}, ${WORKSPACE_DIR} model should read the value of these variables from environment and should not generate these values.\n\n**Before starting any workflow, read environment variables using the provided script:**\n\n```bash\npython ${SKILLS_DIR}/docx/scripts/read_env_vars.py\n```\n\nThis script validates and prints the environment variable values. **Use these values in all subsequent commands** - never hardcode or guess paths.\n\n## Quick Start\n\n**Basic document creation:**\n1. Gather requirements (style, theme, length, tone) - uses `${SKILLS_DIR}/docx/CLARIFICATION.md` or intelligent defaults\n2. Generate outline using search workflow (see Phase 2)\n3. Generate pages in parallel 🤖 - follow orchestration workflow in `${SKILLS_DIR}/docx/workflow_steps/page-orchestration.md` (MANDATORY, spawns page-wise subagents)\n4. Convert JSON to DOCX (see Phase 4):\n```bash\npython ${SKILLS_DIR}/docx/conversion/json_to_docx.py json_pages_dir --output output.docx --theme theme_path","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VbaCZT2x5MAVT4SegakNyh","session_id":"98ef6066-2367-415b-b616-f95ed64be17a","uuid":"efd689ff-a6a2-459f-8d6a-12fc56c3647a"}
