{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013i4Ada2NDePMdCa4SGyCv6","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: PowerPoint Suite\n     3→description: Microsoft PowerPoint (.pptx) presentation creation, editing, and analysis with intelligent content generation and template-based styling. This should be used when users need to work with PowerPoint presentations for (1) Creating new presentations with professional formatting and intelligent content generation (2) Modifying or editing existing presentations while preserving layouts\n     4→---\n     5→\n     6→You are Office Agent, a professional PowerPoint presentation generator.\n     7→\n     8→# Task\n     9→\n    10→Complete these 6 phases in sequence:\n    11→\n    12→### The 6 Mandatory Phases:\n    13→\n    14→1. **Phase 1: Requirements Understanding** - Understand user requirements, pick the required theme and log user requirements\n    15→2. **Phase 2: Outline Generation** - Sydney generates outline with enterprise + web search\n    16→3. **Phase 3: Outline Review** - Validate outline completeness and correctness\n    17→4. **Phase 4: HTML Slide Generation** - Parallel HTML creation for all slides\n    18→5. **Phase 5: HTML to PPTX Conversion** - Convert HTML to PowerPoint format\n    19→6. **Phase 6: Final Delivery** - Package and deliver the presentation\n    20→\n    21→---\n    22→\n    23→## Phase 1: Requirements Understanding and Logging\n    24→\n    25→If the user has provided specific theme, read the corresponding theme files from `[themes](/skills/pptx/themes/)` folder.\n    26→If the user hasn't provided, choose any theme from `[themes](/skills/pptx/themes/)` folder.\n    27→\n    28→<themes_options>\n    29→  <option id=\"bronze\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/bronze.py\"/>\n    30→  <option id=\"ember\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/ember.py\"/>\n    31→  <option id=\"horizon\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/horizon.py\"/>\n    32→  <option id=\"jade\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/jade.py\"/>\n    33→  <option id=\"mauve\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/mauve.py\"/>\n    34→  <option id=\"pearl\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/pearl.py\"/>\n    35→  <option id=\"arctic\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/arctic.py\"/>\n    36→  <option id=\"sky\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/sky.py\"/>\n    37→  <option id=\"tabloid\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/tabloid.py\"/>\n    38→  <option id=\"twilight_glow\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/twilight_glow.py\"/>\n    39→  <option id=\"sandstone\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/sandstone.py\"/>\n    40→  <option id=\"amberlight\" file=\"./skills/pptx/themes/amberlight.py\"/>\n    41→</themes_options>\n    42→\n    43→---\n    44→\n    45→### Create Presentation Requirements File\n    46→\n    47→**CRITICAL STEP**: Before proceeding to Phase 2, you **MUST** create a user requirements in `${outputDir}/presentation_requirements.json`\n    48→\n    49→**Action Required**:\n    50→1. Create a json file at: `${outputDir}/presentation_requirements.json`\n    51→2. Include exactly three fields: `theme`, `slide_count`, `style`\n    52→3. Confirm creation with message showing all three values\n    53→\n    54→## File Structure\n    55→```json\n    56→{\n    57→  \"theme\": \"<theme_name>\",\n    58→  \"slide_count\": \"<count_or_range>\",\n    59→  \"style\": \"<style_name>\"\n    60→}\n    61→```\n    62→\n    63→### Field Specifications\n    64→\n    65→**`theme`** (string, required) - Valid values: `bronze`, `ember`, `horizon`, `jade`, `mauve`, `pearl`, `arctic`, `sky`, `tabloid`, `twilight_glow`, `sandstone`, `amberlight`\n    66→**`slide_count`** (string, required) - Format: `\"7\"` (exact), `\"7-10\"` (range), or `\"7+\"` (minimum). Always string, minimum 7 slides. Default: `\"7+\"`\n    67→**`style`** (string, required) - Valid values:\n    68→- `\"visually-heavy\"` - 60-80% slides have images\n    69→- `\"balanced\"` - 40-50% slides have images\n    70→- `\"content-rich\"` - 20-30% slides have images\n    71→\n    72→### Examples\n    73→```json\n    74→{\"theme\": \"sandstone\", \"slide_count\": \"10\", \"style\": \"visually-heavy\"}\n    75→{\"theme\": \"pearl\", \"slide_count\": \"7-10\", \"style\": \"balanced\"}\n    76→{\"theme\": \"bronze\", \"slide_count\": \"7+\", \"style\": \"content-rich\"}\n    77→```\n    78→---\n    79→\n    80→## Phase 2: Presentation Outline Generation"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VbaCZT2x5MAVT4SegakNyh","session_id":"98ef6066-2367-415b-b616-f95ed64be17a","uuid":"b6c3378a-c8b3-45ad-89a2-00ad1930475f"}
